    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 15. Aphis polaris sp. n., apterous viviparous female. 9, body; 10, frons; 11, antennae; 12, ultimate segments of rostrum; 13, hind tarsus; 14, siphunculus; 15, cauda." ;
